
========================================
  Field Guide Debug Log Server
  Listening on http://127.0.0.1:3947
  Bound to localhost ONLY (not exposed)
  Max entries: 30000
  Max memory:  100 MB
========================================

Endpoints:
  POST /log        Send a log entry
  POST /clear      Clear all entries
  GET  /logs       Retrieve logs (filters: hypothesis, category, since, level, last, deviceId)
                   Add ?format=text for human-readable, ?format=json for JSON array
  GET  /logs/errors   Error-level logs as plain text (deduplicated)
  GET  /logs/summary  Counts by level/category (JSON)
  GET  /health     Server health
  GET  /categories List categories
  GET  /artifacts  List artifact files
  GET  /artifact/<name> Serve file from tools/debug-server/artifacts/
  POST /artifact/<name> Upload file to tools/debug-server/artifacts/
  POST /sync/status  Report sync lifecycle event
  GET  /sync/status  Poll current sync state

Waiting for logs...
